public relations points during a dispute among nato members about 
whether the united states should open early talks on shortrange 
nuclear missiles with the kremlin 
washington would negotiate only after significant reductions in 
soviet conventional weapons while west germany where most of the 
shortrange missiles are based favors talks now 
