three heart attacks genscher has rebounded from his most recent 
bout with illness and the death a few months ago of his 88yearold 
mother 
he was hospitalized in march for surgery to correct a 
urinarytract problem but his staff reports he has returned to his 
grueling 16houraday schedule and has shown no signs of tiring 
