an unofficial observer group that includes former presidents jimmy 
carter and gerald ford 
on saturday carter toured the panama canal and discussed the 
operation of the waterway 
murthas delegation arrived at the us howard air force base to 
avoid the visa requirements and left in three military helicopters 
for an undisclosed location where they will stay 
